arch: rankings, citations, and brand mentions — and why each one tells a different story.</p>\n        <a class=\"post-ctm__link\" href=\"/the-difference-between-mentions-citations-and-rankings/\" >\n          <span class=\"post-ctm__read\">Read more</span><span class=\"post-ctm__arrow\">↗</span>\n        </a>\n      </article>\n\n      <article class=\"post-ctm c2-card\">\n        <div class=\"post-ctm__top\">\n          <h2 class=\"post-ctm__h\">AI Citation Tracking for Small Businesses: How to Measure AI Search Visibility</h2>\n          <div class=\"post-ctm__meta\">\n            <span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">AI</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">AEO</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">SEO</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"post-ctm__p\">A small-business-friendly system for tracking AI citations, brand mentions, and source visibility across ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, and Google AI Overviews.</p>\n        <a class=\"post-ctm__link\" href=\"/ai-citation-tracking-for-small-businesses-how-to-measure-ai-search-visibility/\" >\n          <span class=\"post-ctm__read\">Read more</span><span class=\"post-ctm__arrow\">↗</span>\n        </a>\n      </article>\n\n      <article class=\"post-ctm c2-card\">\n        <div class=\"post-ctm__top\">\n          <h2 class=\"post-ctm__h\">Marketing for Accountants: The Complete Guide</h2>\n          <div class=\"post-ctm__meta\">\n            <span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">Marketing</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">SEO</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">Australia</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"post-ctm__p\">A complete marketing guide for accountants who want better leads, stronger positioning, clearer service pages, and a more reliable client pipeline.</p>\n        <a class=\"post-ctm__link\" href=\"/marketing-for-accountants-the-complete-guide/\" >\n          <span class=\"post-ctm__read\">Read more</span><span class=\"post-ctm__arrow\">↗</span>\n        </a>\n      </article>\n\n      <article class=\"post-ctm c2-card\">\n        <div class=\"post-ctm__top\">\n          <h2 class=\"post-ctm__h\">Marketing for Architects: How Architecture Firms Win Clients</h2>\n          <div class=\"post-ctm__meta\">\n            <span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">Marketing</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">Design</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">Australia</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"post-ctm__p\">How architecture firms can win better-fit clients with sharper positioning, stronger project proof, referral systems, content, and local visibility.</p>\n        <a class=\"post-ctm__link\" href=\"/marketing-for-architects-how-architecture-firms-win-clients/\" >\n          <span class=\"post-ctm__read\">Read more</span><span class=\"post-ctm__arrow\">↗</span>\n        </a>\n      </article>\n\n      <article class=\"post-ctm c2-card\">\n        <div class=\"post-ctm__top\">\n          <h2 class=\"post-ctm__h\">Marketing for Consultants: How to Build a Client Pipeline</h2>\n          <div class=\"post-ctm__meta\">\n            <span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">Marketing</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">Lead</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">Positioning</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"post-ctm__p\">A practical client pipeline guide for consultants, covering positioning, trust-building content, service pages, referrals, and conversion paths.</p>\n        <a class=\"post-ctm__link\" href=\"/marketing-for-consultants-how-to-build-a-client-pipeline/\" >\n          <span class=\"post-ctm__read\">Read more</span><span class=\"post-ctm__arrow\">↗</span>\n        </a>\n      </article>\n\n      <article class=\"post-ctm c2-card\">\n        <div class=\"post-ctm__top\">\n          <h2 class=\"post-ctm__h\">Marketing for Engineers: How Technical Experts Win More Clients</h2>\n          <div class=\"post-ctm__meta\">\n            <span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">Marketing</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">SEO</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">Lead</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"post-ctm__p\">A marketing guide for engineering firms and technical experts who need to translate expertise into trust, visibility, and qualified enquiries.</p>\n        <a class=\"post-ctm__link\" href=\"/marketing-for-engineers-how-technical-experts-win-more-clients/\" >\n          <span class=\"post-ctm__read\">Read more</span><span class=\"post-ctm__arrow\">↗</span>\n        </a>\n      </article>\n\n      <article class=\"post-ctm c2-card\">\n        <div class=\"post-ctm__top\">\n          <h2 class=\"post-ctm__h\">Marketing for Financial Advisers: How to Attract More Clients</h2>\n          <div class=\"post-ctm__meta\">\n            <span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">Marketing</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">SEO</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">Australia</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"post-ctm__p\">How financial advisers can attract more clients with trust-first positioning, compliant content, local SEO, service pages, and stronger proof.</p>\n        <a class=\"post-ctm__link\" href=\"/marketing-for-financial-advisers-how-to-attract-more-clients/\" >\n          <span class=\"post-ctm__read\">Read more</span><span class=\"post-ctm__arrow\">↗</span>\n        </a>\n      </article>\n\n      <article class=\"post-ctm c2-card\">\n        <div class=\"post-ctm__top\">\n          <h2 class=\"post-ctm__h\">Marketing for IT Service Providers: How to Generate More Qualified Leads</h2>\n          <div class=\"post-ctm__meta\">\n            <span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">Marketing</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">SEO</span><span class=\"post-ctm__pill\">B2B SaaS</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"post-ctm__p\">A lead-generation guide for IT service providers, covering positioning, SEO, service pages, proof, offers, and practical demand capture.</p>\n        <a class=\"post-ctm__link\" href=\"/marketing-for-it-service-providers-how-to-generate-more-qualified-leads/\" >\n          <span class=\"post-ctm__read\">Read more</span><span class=\"post-ctm__arrow\">↗</span>\n        </a>\n      </article>\n\n      <div class=\"blog-ctm__empty\" id=\"blogEmpty\" style=\"display:none;\">No posts match that filter.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"blog-ctm__more\">\n      <button class=\"blog-ctm__loadBtn\" id=\"blogLoadMore\" style=\"display: none;\" type=\"button\">\n              Load more    \n      </button>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n    (function () {\n      function initBlogArchive() {\n        const $root = document.getElementById(\"blogArchive\");\n        const $list = document.getElementById(\"blogList\");\n        const $tags = document.getElementById(\"blogTags\");\n        const $moreBtn = document.getElementById(\"blogLoadMore\");\n        const $empty = document.getElementById(\"blogEmpty\");\n\n        if (!$root || !$list || !$tags || !$moreBtn || !$empty) return;\n        if ($root.__blogBound) return;\n        $root.__blogBound = true;\n\n        const PAGE_SIZE = 6;\n        let activeTag = \"All\";\n        let visibleCount = PAGE_SIZE;\n\n        const posts = Array.from($list.querySelectorAll(\".post-ctm\")).map((card) => {\n          const tags = Array.from(card.querySelectorAll(\".post-ctm__pill\"))\n            .map((pill) => (pill.textContent || \"\").trim())\n            .filter(Boolean);\n\n          return { card, tags };\n        });\n\n        function syncActiveTag() {\n          $tags.querySelectorAll(\"[data-tag]\").forEach((btn) => {\n            const tag = btn.getAttribute(\"data-tag\") || \"\";\n            btn.classList.toggle(\"is-active\", tag === activeTag);\n          });\n        }\n\n        function getFilteredPosts() {\n          if (activeTag === \"All\") return posts;\n          return posts.filter((post) => post.tags.includes(activeTag));\n        }\n\n        function renderPosts() {\n          const filtered = getFilteredPosts();\n          const shown = filtered.slice(0, visibleCount);\n\n          posts.forEach((post) => {\n            post.card.style.display = \"none\";\n          });\n\n          if (!shown.length) {\n            $empty.style.display = \"\";\n            $moreBtn.style.display = \"none\";\n            return;\n          }\n\n          $empty.style.display = \"none\";\n\n          shown.forEach((post) => {\n            post.card.style.display = \"\";\n          });\n\n          $moreBtn.style.display = visibleCount >= filtered.length ? \"none\" : \"inline-flex\";\n        }\n\n        $tags.addEventListener(\"click\", function (e) {\n          const btn = e.target.closest(\"[data-tag]\");\n          if (!btn) return;\n\n          e.preventDefault();\n          e.stopPropagation();\n\n          activeTag = btn.getAttribute(\"data-tag\") || \"All\";\n          visibleCount = PAGE_SIZE;\n\n          syncActiveTag();\n          renderPosts();\n        });\n\n        $moreBtn.addEventListener(\"click\", function (e) {\n          e.preventDefault();\n          e.stopPropagation();\n\n          visibleCount += PAGE_SIZE;\n          renderPosts();\n        });\n\n        syncActiveTag();\n        renderPosts();\n      }\n\n      if (document.readyState === \"loading\") {\n        document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", initBlogArchive);\n      } else {\n        initBlogArchive();\n      }\n    })();\n  </script>\n  <br />\n  <br />\n</section>";
